---
layout: base.njk
title: Meetings & Calendar
permalink: /meetings/
description: Notices of Board and membership meetings, agendas, and approved minutes.
---
<p class="lead">Notices of Board and membership meetings, agendas, and approved minutes are posted here. Owners are encouraged to attend.</p>

<h2>Upcoming meetings</h2>
<div class="callout">
  <p style="margin:0"><span class="k">Meeting notices will appear here.</span> Notice of a meeting is also delivered to owners as required by the Bylaws and Texas Property Code <a href="https://statutes.capitol.texas.gov/?tab=1&amp;code=PR&amp;chapter=PR.82" target="_blank" rel="noopener">chapter 82</a>.</p>
</div>

<h2>Annual meeting</h2>
<p>Information about the annual membership meeting — date, location, and how to submit proxies — will be posted here ahead of the meeting each year.</p>

<h2>Approved minutes</h2>
<p class="note">Only <strong>approved</strong> minutes are posted. Draft minutes are not published until the Board approves them.</p>
{% set mins = collections.minutes %}
{% if mins and mins.length %}
<ul class="doc-list">
  {%- for m in mins | reverse %}
  <li><span><span class="doc-name"><a href="{{ m.url }}">{{ m.data.title }}</a></span><span class="doc-meta">{{ m.data.date | longDate }}</span></span></li>
  {%- endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
<p class="note">No approved minutes have been posted yet.</p>
{% endif %}
